archimate:BusinessObject.name: AppliedPartyPenaltyCharge
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation: "The AppliedPartyPenaltyCharge is a type of AppliedPartyBillingCharge. It represents penalty charges such as late fees, payment rejection fees, interests, that could be applied, linked to dunning of a due amount, in order to bill the party according to contractual terms and conditions."
